OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,FKeswick in Bloom is a community group
OL,8,Fwhich charged with the all-important
OL,9,Fjob of keeping Keswick looking
OL,10,Fbeautiful.
OL,12,FIt consists entirely of volunteers who
OL,13,Fcreate and maintain the town's
OL,14,Fflowerbeds and planted areas
OL,15,Fthroughout the year.
OL,17,FBut membership is falling and the
OL,18,Fgroup says its being forced to scale
OL,19,Fback its workload - with the worry it
OL,20,Fmay fold if it doesn't get anyone new
OL,21,Fsigning up.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
