CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783700376
OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,FIt now has just 16 volunteers who are
OL,8,Fgetting older and struggling to manage
OL,9,Fthe physical labour.
OL,11,F"We're all aging, it is an aging
OL,12,Fpopulation in Keswick," said Linda
OL,13,FMallaghan, the chair of Keswick in
OL,14,FBloom.
OL,16,F"It is a commitment but it doesn't
OL,17,Fhave to be a big commitment, an hour a
OL,18,Fweek would be sufficient. If there
OL,19,Fwere two of you - two friends coming
OL,20,Ftogether - it would be brilliant.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783700376
OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,F"If we don't get any volunteers I
OL,8,Fthink we'll have to fold. It's going
OL,9,Fto be a shame because Keswick won't
OL,10,Fhave people doing anything, and you'll
OL,11,Fsee a difference in a few weeks
OL,12,Freally."
OL,14,FAn appeal was made to the June meeting
OL,15,Fof Keswick Town Council that parks
OL,16,Fstaff take over the maintenance of the
OL,17,Fbeds from September when two of KiB's
OL,18,Fmain volunteers step down.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783700376
OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,FThey said its vital they receive some
OL,8,Fsupport in a bid to prevent the area
OL,9,Fdeteriorating.
OL,11,FThe town council said it's committed
OL,12,Fto keeping the group, and its
OL,13,Finvaluable work, afloat. But
OL,14,FCouncillor Claire Peat says its budget
OL,15,Fis affected by the same problem that
OL,16,Fthe group itself is having: fewer
OL,17,Fpeople living in this tourist hotspot
OL,18,Ffull time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
