FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783700376
OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,F"Around a third of the housing in
OL,8,FKeswick is second homes and holiday
OL,9,Flets so the second homes do pay a
OL,10,Fdouble council tax premium, but the
OL,11,Fthe majority of them are holiday lets
OL,12,Fso get business rates relief so don't
OL,13,Fcontribute anything to the Keswick
OL,14,Fpart of the council tax bill," she
OL,15,Fexplained.
OL,17,F"There are full streets in Keswick
OL,18,Fwhich don't have full time residents
OL,19,Fon them so we've just got this small
OL,20,Fpool.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
