FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1783700376
OL,3,CKeswick in Bloom struggling for
OL,4,Cvolunteers to help keep town looking
OL,5,Cits best
OL,7,F"Our parks teams are kept really busy
OL,8,Fwith the work they already do so we
OL,9,Fwill do what we can in the mean time
OL,10,Fbefore we then have to look at whether
OL,11,Fthere's any room in the budget to look
OL,12,Fat contractors to help with the the
OL,13,Fwork that's needed to stay on top of
OL,14,Fthings."
